                    <span>at the beginning of each year, i always contemplate "my next big move". i just bought this book and though i'm only halfway through it, the advice has been really practical, sensible, and most importantly, achievable for the average woman, like me. and it's written with great style and personality. thank god someone has finally written this book! if i ever do start my own business, this book will be my Gospel.</span>
                  
              
